<div class="h3"><h3>I’m not sure you can go wrong on the island, as there are only 40 hotels, but whether you choose a hotel or rent out your own villa, you are sure to find a gorgeous view! I’d pick it based on location (if you want to be in the center or not) and of course, price.</h3>
